metadata.Readme:
Sitecore Forms Extensions is an add-on to Sitecore Forms. This packages is compatible with Sitecore 9.3 and Sitecore 10
Documentation on http://onelittlespark.bartverdonck.be/sitecoreformsextentions/
Source code on https://github.com/bartverdonck/Sitecore-Forms-Extensions
The package includes: * Robot Detection Component * Google Captcha Component * RawHtml Component * HiddenField Component * Azure Blob Storage file storage provider * Advanced Send Mail submit action * Jump to page submit action * Identify Contact submit action * Subscribe to list submit action * Date Timespan Validators * Value Providers for xDB facets * Value Provider store back * Value Provider conditions
